            "about_body": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>Bacii was born from the beautiful chaos of childhood. Created by a mum of two boys, Bacii began with a simple idea: children&#39;s clothing should feel as playful, expressive and unique as the little people wearing it.</p><p>When I couldn&#39;t find pieces that felt fun without being over the top, and elevated without losing personality, I decided to create them. Designed in Australia and made from premium organic cotton, Bacii combines playful graphics, thoughtful colours and relaxed silhouettes made for everyday adventures — from playgrounds and park dates to snack breaks and sofa cuddles.</p>",
